attributionInfo.brokerName: Keller Williams Premier Realty Lake Minnetonka

data.description: Rare opportunity to own in this quality condo building.  Superbly convenient and quiet. Walking distance to Luce Line Trail System, Medicine Lake & trails.  Stunning renovation features all new flooring and custom lighting. Striking updates to fireplace surround. Gorgeous granite counters, tile backsplash, ample cabinetry, new stainless steel appliances provide a great setting for food prep and entertaining. Open, inviting floor plan. Large primary suite has walk-in closet, ensuite full bath & balcony access with peaceful views.  Plenty of natural light throughout. Large junior bedroom has extensive closet space.  Additional full bath and laundry with new washer/dryer. Two garage stalls and storage in underground, heated garage guest parking in front of charming building. Elevator. Wayzata Schools. Sellers will pre-pay 6 months of Association Fees.
